---
title: American-Style Haloumi Schnitzels with Potato Wedges & Smokey Slaw
description: Golden crusted chicken schnitzels get a boost of flavour with our All-American spice blend! Serve up a side of potato
wedges plus a crisp and colourful slaw for a bright and tasty dinner that brings fun and flavour to the table.
